{"tid":813350,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲覺得拍緊拖永遠做主動會好攰？","createTime":"2018-09-10T11:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T17:59:24.000Z","uid":5292,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f46210a845817510026e7f12602d74d812a936ba","tid":813350,"uid":5292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T11:14:14.000Z","msg":"咁岩見到有個post話女仔會好依賴日日同佢傾計既男仔<br />\n<br />\n有時真係唔知對方想點<br />\n下下都要自己做主動<br />\n好似自己同自己拍拖咁<br />\n<br />\n睇戲睇邊套又無所謂<br />\n食飯食咩又無所謂<br />\n去邊玩黎黎去去都係行下街<br />\n咁就過左一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時會消失一兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時就好sweet 識嗲下人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大半時間都係度諗<br />\n究竟係咪<br />\n一個人 從鏡內發展恩愛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15dfaa3bb5128ec2dc5f7ca8868fcd47c8459f9f","tid":813350,"uid":207574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T11:33:50.000Z","msg":"然之後分手嗰陣就會覺得其實係咪已經比哂 signal 我佢無哂 feel"},{"pid":"47af64be75d501284dfd215f4e9b311ada4d7e27","tid":813350,"uid":5292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15dfaa3bb5128ec2dc5f7ca8868fcd47c8459f9f","tid":813350,"uid":207574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T11:33:50.000Z","msg":"然之後分手嗰陣就會覺得其實係咪已經比哂 signal 我佢無哂 feel"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T11:35:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724f21394f0d98520609bd2ad9275a6fd20e6d47","tid":813350,"uid":53592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:47:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class